<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>로그인</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #5E72E4;
            --secondary-color: #525f7f;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .btn {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .custom-container {
            max-width: 540px;
        }

        .custom-card {
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .custom-card-header {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            border-top-left-radius: 1rem;
            border-top-right-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .custom-card-body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 1rem;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .custom-btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .custom-btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #4962D9;
            border-color: #4962D9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<section class="d-flex vh-100 justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="container custom-container">
        <div class="card custom-card">
            <div class="card-header custom-card-header text-white text-center">
                <h2>HELLO 게시판</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body custom-card-body p-5">
                <p class="text-secondary text-center mb-4">게시판을 이용하려면 로그인을 해주세요!</p>

                <div class = "mb-2">
                    <a href="/oauth2/authorization/google">
                        <img src="/img/google.png">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
